                <p>  <strong><em> -Harry Potter- </em> </strong> </p>
                    <img width="450" height="300" src="https://www.filmarasidergisi.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/harry-potter.jpg" border="1" alt="Harry potter görseli" title="Görsel">
